{"tid":878141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[賽跑冠軍] 汀角路七旬翁過馬路捱的士撞　昏迷送院","createTime":"2018-10-27T01:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T03:21:47.000Z","uid":6497,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3efd3ce0da074ef9ec2b6a1df2b5f185e4a13886","tid":878141,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T01:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181027/s00001/fef59b05acfa6b902a4d8baa13eb2e0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181027%2Fs00001%2Ffef59b05acfa6b902a4d8baa13eb2e0a.jpg&h=b9227f19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凌晨3時許，一架新界的士載客沿大埔汀角路往大美督方向行駛，駛至近大貴街交界時，一名75歲姓邵老伯突然打斜衝出馬路，的士收掣不及將他撞飛5米外倒地昏迷，涼鞋亦飛脫。的士車頭左邊車牌、車頭玻璃及車頭大燈損毀，64歲姓葉的士司機無受傷，救護員到場將昏迷老伯送院搶救，老伯其後需接受手術診治，家人趕赴醫院了解。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場調查，其間使用正在測試的360全景相機，協助拍攝現場環境及搜證。"},{"pid":"a5b3abd90533a4101fb6e07f46c07bd53a8deca1","tid":878141,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:34:51.000Z","msg":"又死一件廢種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0242b78722c0fca684ee4f268e98a4e6cd0dc67","tid":878141,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:42:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b3f942303b275ba9cb17363fe6a749411c06cb4","tid":878141,"uid":1221,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/134444_208c493f71090cc5d40c6f42b018693f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F134444_208c493f71090cc5d40c6f42b018693f.gif&h=cff1c081&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n趕住去死"}]}